clinical_trials.eligibility_criteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

* female aged between 18-45 y old;
* SF \<80 µg/L;
* BMI 18.5-24.9 kg/m2;
* weight \<70 kg;
* signed informed consent;
* able to communicate and comprehend English language

Exclusion Criteria:

* anemia (Hb \<12 g/dL);
* inflammation (CRP \> 5 mg/L);
* chronic digestive, renal
